{"tid":1515482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班IVE仔同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:50:23.000Z","uid":264538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33258bac2aa99b377e1bb18c1fcbd645bf468c49","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"8月5號叫人罷工叫得咁撚大聲<br />\n依加叫你罷兩日課你就驚自己出席唔夠<br />\n有幾多人因為罷工而被辭職呀屌你老母<br />\n依加你班仆街係咪罷課都唔撚敢<br />\n罷課都要番學拍撚左卡先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母果陣叫人罷工就番少日唔會死<br />\n依加你地仆街呢罷兩日課就驚retake<br />\n咁被辭職果啲人點算呀當佢地condom呀<br />\n咁果日罷工人地有冇話罷做不罷工呀<br />\n有冇話番公司拍左卡先啦我地坐係到唔做野咪得<br />\n人地利益就冇所謂自己出席率就好重要<br />\n我屌撚哂你班仆街呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母比啲骨氣得唔得呀香港人</span></strong></span><br />\n罷課唔拍卡都唔敢你仲夠膽做啲咩<br />\n已經唔係叫你上去食子彈啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷課就咪撚拍卡直接去百萬大道</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNhJTBx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNhJTBx.png&h=41de8a3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2db48f54c053ae8192052b099bee30659918d27","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:23:10.000Z","msg":"直接去集會"},{"pid":"695c61def2e76d281861cd9298bcdcdd765fb253","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"直接去集會"},{"pid":"d9432c706365ed5dc70cc89dbaf2b5a73759d621","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:23:42.000Z","msg":"直接去集會"},{"pid":"218b08980384cc5183095aeec02bda00df45f45c","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"直接去集會"},{"pid":"3eb4e85ba4745a1c94bf7f18c13bb93dcd404319","tid":1515482,"uid":264538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef8833b